        "@value": "ALT CTRL - Starring: Jeremy Taggart, Patrick Pentland, and Andre Pettipas"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Welcome to your Supergroup Therapy Class. ALT CTRL is a band consisting of Jeremy Taggart formerly of Our Lady Peace, Patrick Pentland of Sloan, up-and-coming frontman, Andre Pettipas and a rotating cast of world class players. They bring the nostalgia and MUSIC of the 90's greatest hits to life.</p>\n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n</style>\n\n"
      }
    ],
