  {
    "@id": "https://ticketpro.ca/event/1686263864",
    "@type": [
      "http://schema.org/Event"
    ],
    "http://schema.org/startDate": [
      {
        "@type": "http://schema.org/Date",
        "@value": "2026-05-16T19:30:00-03:00"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/location": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ticketpro.ca/place/55150121"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/image": [
      {
        "@id": "https://tproatlantic.ticketpro.ca/api/v1/resources/1686265518.jpeg?version=1"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/offers": [
      {
        "@id": "_:g781580"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww3.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=10711"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww3.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=10711"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Green Room Session with Claire Porter - Special Guest Evan AuCoin"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p><BIG><b>Special Guest Evan AuCoin</b></BIG></p>\n\n<p>Join us for an intimate night of live music in the Green Room, featuring Newfoundland powerhouse Claire Porter with special guest Evan AuCoin.</p>\n\n<p>Fresh off double nominations at the 2026 East Coast Music Awards, Claire Porter brings her signature blend of sharp wit, masterful musicianship, and genre-bending sound to the stage. With a voice that carries both power and nuance, her songs—equal parts heartfelt and unexpected—create a performance that feels as personal as it is captivating.</p>\n\n<p>Joining her is acclaimed singer-songwriter Evan AuCoin, known for his rich storytelling and deeply authentic sound. Blending folk, country, blues, and traditional Newfoundland influences, AuCoin delivers songs that resonate with honesty and emotional depth, whether in stripped-down acoustic moments or soaring full-bodied arrangements.</p>\n\n<p>Together, these two dynamic artists promise a night of connection, storytelling, and exceptional musicianship in the unique, up-close setting of the Green Room Session series.</p>\n\n<p>Don't miss this chance to experience two of Atlantic Canada's rising voices in an evening designed for music lovers.</p>\n\n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n</style>\n\n"
      }
    ],
