    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Kyla Cobbler: Gone Rogue"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>In her debut show <i>Gone Rogue</i>, Kyla covers everything from the chaos of Barcelona dating life to navigating a friend crush and the power plays of a barbeque. Kyla brings fearless honesty, quickfire wit, and a knack for spinning real-life chaos into killer stories. With a fiercely loyal fanbase, explosive stage presence, and a rapidly expanding global profile, Kyla Cobbler is not just a rising star—she's a force to be reckoned with..</p>\n"
      }
    ],
