    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Menopause The Musical"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p><b><font color='#6400cb'>The Original Smash Hit</font><br>\n<font color='#b801c5'>Menopause The Musical</font><br>\n<font color='#6400cb'>Returns To Spatz Theatre</font></b></p>\n\n<p><b><font color='#ca0605'>Tues.  April 21 @ 7:30 p.m.</font>  <br>\n<font color='#2c6600'>1 Show Only - Don't Miss Out!</font><br>\n<font color='#9a5200'>Canadian All- Star Cast !</font></b></p>\n\n<p>The hysterical world wide hit, 'Menopause The Musical' is finally returning to Spatz Theatre for just 1 show only.</p>\n\n<p>Come laugh away your Tuesday evening & see what millions of women have been raving & cheering about for years!</p>\n\n<p>Set in Bloomingdale's department store, 4 women with nothing in common but a black lace bra... come to realize they have more to share than ever imagined.</p>\n\n<p>Staged to 25 classic hits from the '60s, '70s and '80s the All-Star Canadian cast makes fun of their hot flashes, night sweats, mood swings, wrinkles, not enough sex, too much sex, chocolate binges and more!</p>\n\n<p>'Menopause' is hilarious & leaves you singing & dancing in the aisles, guaranteed! </p>\n\n<p>Come Celebrate Your Womanhood & Join The Sisterhood!</p>\n\n<p><b><font color='#6400cb'>Bring your Mother, Daughter, Sister and Friends!</font></b></p>\n\n<p><b><font color='#2c6600'>Voted Las Vegas - 2016 Entertainer Of The Year!</font></b></p>\n\n<p>Ask anyone who saw it - they loved it!</p>\n\n<p>Rated : Best Off-Broadway Musical Comedy</p>\n\n<p><i>'It's impossible not to laugh!'</i> - THE NEW YORK TIMES</p>\n\n<p><i>'Fresh, funny and simply terrific!'</i> - LA TIMES</p>\n\n<p><i>'A true celebration of women!'</i> - TORONTO STAR</p>\n\n<p><i>'Dollar for Dollar...It's the best show in town!'</i> - LAS VEGAS REVIEW JOURNAL</p>\n\n<p><i>'Ninety minutes of pure fun!'</i> - TORONTO SUN</p>\n\n<p><i>'Woman Need This!'</i> - THE TODAY SHOW</p>\n\n<p><b>Rated: Man-datory Viewing For Men! :)</b></p>"
      }
    ],
