    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "SoPA Spring Showcase Concert"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>The highlight of the year at Holland College's School of Performing Arts (SoPA) is the Spring Showcase concert. ALL current SoPA students will be on stage throughout the night as we present our 1st-year R&B and Pop ensembles, along with our 2nd-year Jazz and Latin ensembles! There will be a few special surprises on the bill as well.</p>\n\n<p>Come out and cheer on these talented students as they celebrate another year of learning and performing. This year's group of students includes musicians from PEI, NB, Ontario, Russia, China, and Taiwan.</p>\n\n<p>Tickets are $20+fees and can be purchased through TicketPro.</p>\n\n<p>We hope you can join us at the beautiful Florence Simmons Performance Hall on April 23!</p>\n\n"
      }
    ],
