    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "THE GOOD BROTHERS - 50th Anniversary Tour"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>The Osprey proudly welcomes 8x Juno Winners, the Good Brothers on their 50th Anniversary Tour. Brothers Bruce, Brian and Larry Good continue to deliver a world-class show that features their trademark sibling harmonies. In addition to their Juno Awards, this legendary group are inductees to both the Canadian and North American Country Music Halls of Fame and have headlined gigs at Massey Hall, Roy Thompson Hall, The National Art Centre and countless shows at LA's Universal Amphitheatre with their mentor, Gordon Lightfoot. Don't miss this opportunity to experience this historic show at your very own Osprey Arts Centre.</p>\n\n<style>\n    .titleTax {\n       display: none !important;\n   }\n</style>\n\n"
      }
    ],
